Package: PostGWAS
Type: Package
Title: African-Ancestry-First Post-GWAS Utilities with PLINK2 PGEN Support
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure",
           email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Donghyung", family = "Lee",
           email = "leed13@miamioh.edu", role = c("ctb"),
           comment = "Original GAUSS summary-statistic methods")
    )
Description: African-ancestry-first post-GWAS utilities for working directly
    with PLINK2 '.pgen', '.pvar', and '.psam' reference panels. Provides
    population-aware keep-file derivation from '.psam' metadata, native
    'pgenlibr'-backed population-weighted LD estimation, and summary-statistic
    imputation workflows that avoid package-specific intermediate genotype files.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0),
    GAUSS.pgen
Encoding: UTF-8
